  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    A coordinate class, containing information on a point on a map (used by the A* path finding algorithm in the Simulation classes)
    Menu
    A menu for the Multi-Robot Simulation program
    Robot
    A simulated robot which takes part in an exploration simulation.
    Run
    Runs the robot exploration simulations
    Simulation
    A Simulation Program to test Multi-Robot Exploration of a Map, it is thread safe
    SimulationThread
    A thread which is created to run a robot exploration simulation
